{"tid":1620810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(注意安全) 邊爐GAS罐","createTime":"2019-10-04T11:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T12:15:12.000Z","uid":62290,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a2029447204fe1d250100992dc2afe1ac8e757","tid":1620810,"uid":62290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"近排天氣轉涼左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都係時間開始入定啲邊爐氣以防萬一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以打邊爐燒下啲畜牲肉食下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又或者加個轉換頭就可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">噴火取下暖</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要係<strong>又平又細枝,帶出街都唔覺</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">**不過大家要注意安全bor,你知啦,呢啲壓縮氣體罐, 一唔覺意dum左出去可能會爆嫁嘛</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">係本身有火既地方用就仲危險</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hongkong.pricerite.com.hk/media/catalog/product/cache/2/image/407x407/b94598f365e1e33537597098c978f2c8/1/1/114875_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhongkong.pricerite.com.hk%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2F2%2Fimage%2F407x407%2Fb94598f365e1e33537597098c978f2c8%2F1%2F1%2F114875_1.jpg&h=ac67e285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hongkong.pricerit